<title>AA ZUAMMI KHRIHFA BU CH386</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 A hlat a nai, Khrihfabu-mi Pumh awkah ra chuak cio tuah u,
 Ruah-channak le lung-lawmhnak in Pathian bia kha ngai cio tuah u,

[C1]
   Aa zuammi Khrihfabu, Jesuh sin aa pummi, Lungkhat thinkhat tein, A
   min liannak chim u; Pathian pennak caah, Zuam cio ko tuah u si; Kan
   Khrihfabu hmunhnak thlacam zungzal u si.

[V2]
 Kan Siangpahrang Thangthatnak hla Sak awk caah, kan i pum i Mino zong
 nih Pathian sinah, Zungzal lu-nunnak kha an hmuh,

[C2]
   Aa zuammi Khrihfabu, Jesuh sin aa pummi, Lungkhat thinkhat tein, A
   min liannak chim u; Pathian pennak caah, Zuam cio ko tuah u si; Kan
   Khrihfabu hmunhnak thlacam zungzal u si.

[V3]
 Kan Bawi riantuan, I tlaih ko u Kan biakamnak kha remh than u, Amah
 sin vancung phak hlan tiang, Zumh karhnak in rian tuan u si.

[C3]
   Aa zuammi Khrihfabu, Jesuh sin aa pummi, Lungkhat thinkhat tein, A
   min liannak chim u; Pathian pennak caah, Zuam cio ko tuah u si; Kan
   Khrihfabu hmunhnak thlacam zungzal u si.</lyrics>
<key>C</key>
</song>